title.narrative: Jordan First Equitable Growth & Job Creation Programmatic Development Policy Financing

description.narrative: The program development objective is to support Jordan to set foundations to: (i) reduce business costs and improve market accessibility, (ii) create more flexible and integrated labor markets and provide better and more efficient social assistance, and (iii) improve fiscal sustainability and take more informed decisions regarding risk.
